  Macro mac_BitCount8(val)
    Protected cnt.i            
    cnt= Bool(val& $1)  + Bool(val&   $2)+ Bool(val&   $4)+ Bool(val&   $8)+
         Bool(val&$10)  + Bool(val&  $20)+ Bool(val&  $40)+ Bool(val&  $80)+
    ProcedureReturn cnt
  EndMacro

